{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "7c64aae5-434f-4dea-a86e-bc2460986814", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/7c64aae5-434f-4dea-a86e-bc2460986814@1.pkg/1772602405264/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602405589", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/7c64aae5-434f-4dea-a86e-bc2460986814@1.pkg/1772602405264/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602405589"}, "identifier": "7c64aae5-434f-4dea-a86e-bc2460986814", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>《使至塞上》是唐代诗人王维奉命赴边疆慰问将士途中所作的一首纪行诗，记述出使塞上的旅程以及旅程中所见的塞外风光。“大漠孤烟直，长河落日圆”表达了诗人对守边战士的爱国精神以及边塞奇异风光的赞美之情，并非是哀婉消沉之情。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是（　　）</p>\n\n<p>【甲】使至塞上&nbsp;王维</p>\n\n<p>单车欲问边，属国过居延。征蓬出汉塞，归雁入胡天。</p>\n\n<p>大漠孤烟直，长河落日圆。萧关逢候骑，都护在燕然。</p>\n\n<p>【乙】战城南&nbsp;杨炯</p>\n\n<p>塞北途辽远，城南战苦辛。幡旗如鸟翼，甲胄似鱼鳞。</p>\n\n<p>冻水寒伤马，悲风愁杀人。寸心明白日①，千里暗黄尘。</p>\n\n<p>【注释】①白日：喻指君主。</p>\n", "title": "下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是（　　）【甲】使至塞上 王维单车欲问边，属国过居延。征蓬出汉塞，归雁入胡天。大漠孤烟直，长河落日圆。萧关逢候骑，都护在燕然。【乙】战城南 杨炯塞北途辽远，城南战苦辛。幡旗如鸟翼，甲胄似鱼鳞。冻水寒伤马，悲风愁杀人。寸心明白日①，千里暗黄尘。【注释】①白日：喻指君主。", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/7c64aae5-434f-4dea-a86e-bc2460986814@1.pkg/item.json?v=1752939682171", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>《使至塞上》以大漠、秋景为背景，用征蓬、归雁、孤烟等景物，组成一幅塞外风光图。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>《战城南》颔联通过典型景物“幡旗”“甲胄”来描绘战场景象。不但写出了军队的威武，而且写出了士兵的斗志。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>《使至塞上》颈联雄浑开阔，诗中有画，堪称千古绝句，体现这首诗歌哀婉消沉的艺术特色。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>《战城南》尾联表现了征战者心中始终充满明亮的阳光，心系祖国，视死如归，报效君王的情怀。</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是（　　）</p>\n\n<p>【甲】使至塞上&nbsp;王维</p>\n\n<p>单车欲问边，属国过居延。征蓬出汉塞，归雁入胡天。</p>\n\n<p>大漠孤烟直，长河落日圆。萧关逢候骑，都护在燕然。</p>\n\n<p>【乙】战城南&nbsp;杨炯</p>\n\n<p>塞北途辽远，城南战苦辛。幡旗如鸟翼，甲胄似鱼鳞。</p>\n\n<p>冻水寒伤马，悲风愁杀人。寸心明白日①，千里暗黄尘。</p>\n\n<p>【注释】①白日：喻指君主。</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "5036342747", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLI